title: The Power of Clarity
itunes:title: The Power of Clarity
description:
Episode 135 - Want to know the main reason people don't hit their goals? Because they are not clear on EXACTLY what they want. They have a general idea but the never know in detail exactly what they want. In this episode I talk about the two main reasons why clarity is such a power part of hitting your goals.
